00:19:34,310 --> 00:19:37,810
And the duty to establish
justice is yours!

250
00:19:39,210 --> 00:19:41,190
Hence overcome your weakness

251
00:19:42,210 --> 00:19:47,060
and prepare for this battle!

252
00:20:00,980 --> 00:20:03,150
But murders shall occur
at my hands, Krishna!

253
00:20:05,010 --> 00:20:06,920
If lives are ended by me

254
00:20:08,710 --> 00:20:11,250
won't that destroy
the compassion within me?

255
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:16,150
And if compassion
is the basis of justice

256
00:20:17,840 --> 00:20:20,950
won't my soul become unjust?

257
00:20:31,980 --> 00:20:35,420
The limit of justice
is surely created.

258
00:20:37,140 --> 00:20:40,060
But the limit of actions
isn't created, Arjun.

259
00:20:42,380 --> 00:20:45,980
The difference between
actions and deeds

260
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,650
is necessary to be understood.

261
00:20:50,140 --> 00:20:54,850
All deeds are actions,
but all actions aren't deeds.

262
00:20:56,780 --> 00:20:58,690
A deed is an action

263
00:20:59,410 --> 00:21:02,020
for which an outcome
is expected.

264
00:21:03,980 --> 00:21:05,890
When one carries out a deed

265
00:21:06,110 --> 00:21:10,960
expecting pleasure,
wealth and praise

266
00:21:12,210 --> 00:21:14,990
he is bound by the outcome
of that action.

267
00:21:16,410 --> 00:21:20,290
When a deed is performed with
an expectation of an outcome

268
00:21:20,780 --> 00:21:23,150
it is called 'Sakam Karma Yoga'.*
*Self-centred action.

269
00:21:23,940 --> 00:21:28,760
And when a deed is carried out
without expecting an outcome

270
00:21:28,810 --> 00:21:31,290
it is called 'Nishkaam Karma Yoga'.*
*Self-less or desireless action: action performed without any expectation of fruits or results, and the central tenet of Karma Yoga path to Liberation.

271
00:21:32,840 --> 00:21:36,650
This is the very reason
he has to be born repeatedly.

272
00:21:38,080 --> 00:21:40,850
In reality a man isn't
bound by a deed.

273
00:21:42,040 --> 00:21:45,250
The expectations linked to
that deed is what bounds him.

